       <div class="span8 dotted-top" role="main">
        <div id="quicksearch" style="vertical-align: baseline;">
         <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">
          Search policies:
         </h3>
         <p>
          Enter keywords to match the policy title or policy number (if any):
         </p>
         <form action="/advanced-search.php" id="form_search" method="get" name="form_search">
          <input name="action" type="hidden" value="search"/>
          <input name="op" type="hidden" value="results"/>
          <input name="lookup" type="hidden" value="1"/>
          <div>
           <input class="text_small" id="keywords" maxlength="255" name="keywords" style="height: 2em; vertical-align: middle; width: 70%;" type="text"/>
          </div>
          <div style="float: right; margin-top: -55px;">
           <input class="btn-blue" name="search" type="submit" value="Search"/>
          </div>
         </form>
        </div>
        <div style="clear: left;">
         <p>
          For a more specific search, use
          <a href="http://policy.ucop.edu/advanced-search.php?action=search">
           advanced search
          </a>
          .
         </p>
         <p>
          Policies accessed from this site are current and maintained by the
          <a href="http://ucop.edu/ethics-compliance-audit-services/policy">
           University Policy Office
          </a>
          .
         </p>
         <p>
          Academic Personnel policies (the
          <em>
           Academic Personnel Manual
          </em>
          ) are available from the
          <a href="http://www.ucop.edu/academic-personnel/index.html">
           Academic Personnel website
          </a>
          .  Regents' policies can be found on the
          <a href="http://regents.universityofcalifornia.edu/governance/policies/index.html" target="_blank">
           Regents' Policy website
          </a>
          .
         </p>
        </div>
        <div class="dotted-cols">
